&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Consultant Physician&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are seeking a Consultant Community Physician to join our friendly teams in rural west Kent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Based in idyllic Tonbridge, you will provide expert support as part of our innovative Home Treatment Service, as well as taking responsibility for acute ill and recovering patients in our community hospitals and across the health and social care sectors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will lead a team of doctors who are dedicated to adult and elderly care, actively managing patients living with frailty and other complex conditions in their homes and hospitals and working closely with clinical, social and external partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You’ll need to be flexible, creative and ready to embrace new ways of working as we continue to invest in the community sector. In return we’ll offer you a fantastic role in a relaxed and welcoming environment that gives you the opportunity to expand your knowledge and skills. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Although this is a full time post, candidates wanting to work less than full time or flexibly are welcomed. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post attracts a generous golden handshake and/or a Recruitment and retention premia payment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Find out more about our clinical roles in west Kent &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;visit kentcht.nhs.uk/careers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interviews will be held on 7th December 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information please contact&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
